'''第48屆坎城影展'''於[[1995年電影|1995年]]5月17日（法國當地時間）至5月28日舉行。本屆[[坎城電影節|坎城電影節]]評審團主席是[[法國|法國]][[演員|演員]][[珍妮·摩露|珍妮·摩露]]，[[金棕櫚獎|金棕櫚獎]]則由[[塞爾維亞|塞爾維亞]]導演[[艾米爾·庫斯杜力卡|艾米爾·庫斯杜力卡]]獲得<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/archives/1995/allAward.html|title=Awards 1995 : All Awards|accessdate=2013-12-10|archive-date=2016-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818201935/http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/archives/1995/allAward.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

本屆坎城影展開幕片是[[尚-皮爾·桑里|尚-皮爾·桑里]]與{{link-fr|馬克·卡侯|Marc Caro}}合導的《{{link-fr|驚異狂想曲|La cité des enfants perdus}}》<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/U-S-Films-Top-Lineup-At-Cannes-Festival-48th-3035051.php|title=U.S. Films Top Lineup At Cannes Festival / 48th annual event begins May 17|accessdate=2013-12-10|work=The San Francisco Chronicle|first=Christopher|last=Burns|date=1995-04-26|archive-date=2020-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326190234/https://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/U-S-Films-Top-Lineup-At-Cannes-Festival-48th-3035051.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.apnewsarchive.com/1995/Cannes-Film-Festival-Opens/id-8dc6837e376a63941acf4dcb7c0c7126|title=CANNES FILM FESTIVAL OPENS|accessdate=2013-12-10|archive-date=2017-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171129072349/http://www.apnewsarchive.com/1995/Cannes-Film-Festival-Opens/id-8dc6837e376a63941acf4dcb7c0c7126|dead-url=no}}</ref>，閉幕片是[[山姆·雷米|山姆·雷米]]執導《[[致命的快感|致命的快感]]》<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/the-man-from-cannes-says-yes-1617259.html|title=The man from Cannes says yes|accessdate=2013-12-10|location=London|work=The Independent|date=1995-04-27|archive-date=2020-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326190214/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/the-man-from-cannes-says-yes-1617259.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

